== Changelog ==
= 1.3.3 =
* Added small tag styling
* Removed monthly limit on Sitemap template
* Fixed bug with tax_query being overwritten
* Recent project footer titles are now links
* Removed stats code option
* Adding missing translations to template

= 1.3.2 =
* Fixed 'with sidebar' template in IE8
* Added Google+ icon
* Fixed bug with nested comment display

= 1.3.1 =
* Fixed FitVids to cap video embed size if user specifies it
* Stylistic updates to categories on archives page

= 1.3 =
* Made 'no posts found' text translatable
* Added page template with sidebar
* Added multiple project page support via [gallery] shortcode
* Hiding 'leave a comment' link when comments are disabled
* Fixed blockquote styling that conflicted with featured images
* Added FitVids JavaScript to make responsive videos cleaner
* Fixed image stretching in old versions of Internet Explorer

= 1.2.1 =
* Fixed some bugs in the attachment template

= 1.2 =
* Fixed content width to "full" when no thumbnail is set on a page or post
* Fixed footer spacing when there are multiple widgets
* Allowing comments on pages and gallery/project posts

= 1.1 =
* Added support for galleries/attachments on posts
* Various spacing fixes/cleanup
* Made long post titles wrap instead of running into sidebar
* Added indicator for sticky posts
* Added styling for tables and definition lists
* Added dropdown menu support

= 1.0.1 =
* Use an <h3> so the title in the fallback sidebar is properly styled.

= 1.0 =
* Initial release!